{"tid":484740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呂麗瑤前教練：驚講錯嘢　到時麻煩　要請律師先","createTime":"2017-11-30T10:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T13:17:15.000Z","uid":26769,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5230d92d373b461ed5c7f0fb5ed30f79b3a3db","tid":484740,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/sZE79B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsZE79B&d=E0Za%2BMemw7y9CMrK2FtVZMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2d4f61f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/sZE79B</a><br />\n<br />\n「香港欄后」呂麗瑤凌晨在Facebook貼出文章，指自己於初中時曾被教練性侵犯，事件引起廣泛關注；呂麗瑤的現任教練鄧漢昇今早接受電台訪問之後，《香港01》找到呂麗瑤其中一位前教練，欲了解他對事件看法，及曾否聽到呂麗瑤談及事件。這位前教練起初指「唔想講嘢」，及後指「驚講錯多到時麻煩，要請律師先。」<br />\n<br />\n呂麗瑤事件引爆後，記者獨家找到她其中一位前教練訪問，他表示，對事件不清楚，又指怕講多會錯，「要請律師先」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，發現當年呂麗瑤就讀培正中學時，田徑隊共有三位教練，記者聯絡到其中一位教練，希望了解當時有否留意到呂麗瑤有異樣，以及曾否聽聞或知悉事件。<br />\n<br />\n前教練承認曾為田徑教練，被問及有否聽聞呂麗瑤事件時，他表示「唔想講嘢，驚講錯嘢，到時有麻煩，要請律師先。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者：想問（你）之前係咪做過田徑教練？<br />\n前教練：係。<br />\n記者：有無聽聞「呂麗瑤性侵事件」？<br />\n前教練：我唔想講嘢，因為點解呢，我驚講嘢呢，講錯或者唔知點樣，到時就好麻煩，因為我要請律師先。<br />\n記者：但你有無聽聞過呢件事？<br />\n前教練：聽聞過。<br />\n記者：你曾經係佢教練，知唔知真係有人曾經性侵過佢？<br />\n前教練：咁我又真係唔知喎。<br />\n記者：佢有無向你吐過苦水？<br />\n前教練：呢個我都唔清楚，我唔知。<br />\n記者：我見到（屈臣氏）田徑（總會）網頁，阿sir都除咗名，會唔會知係咩原因？<br />\n前教練：可能都係呢啲事。<br />\n記者：點為之呢啲事？<br />\n前教練：即係你話睇見呢段新聞，不過真係唔好意思，我宜家好亂。<br />\n記者：佢有無向你尋求幫助？<br />\n前教練：我真係唔知，唔好意思，唔該你。"},{"pid":"3e03ce2fc34143aec377a7e1e9d2115bfb718273","tid":484740,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1836fc27940f475867e78d9c16ca19a6828149e7","tid":484740,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5e451babc302f3cfd85ee38052c9ac5f5d7ca2eb","tid":484740,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"請咩律師咁勁三個禮拜都請唔到？"},{"pid":"2a9ab6ac8107433655c4032ff5ec6a54b07d5af5","tid":484740,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47e8bb094c3a02047b2b90b392239b6688b46b0b","tid":484740,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"女例搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e23532bb48b8769342505f81be030a528818b8","tid":484740,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，最新確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">newlife</span></del>、JR、RedBaron = Epiphany、dewi、bbchu、D_Wa